 317:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/lv_math.c ****      * Fast XY vector to integer degree algorithm - Jan 2011 www.RomanBlack.com
 318:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/lv_math.c ****      * Converts any XY values including 0 to a degree value that should be
 319:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/lv_math.c ****      * within +/- 1 degree of the accurate value without needing
 320:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/lv_math.c ****      * large slow trig functions like ArcTan() or ArcCos().
 321:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/lv_math.c ****      * NOTE! at least one of the X or Y values must be non-zero!
 322:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/lv_math.c ****      * This is the full version, for all 4 quadrants and will generate
 323:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/lv_math.c ****      * the angle in integer degrees from 0-360.
 324:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/lv_math.c ****      * Any values of X and Y are usable including negative values provided
 325:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/lv_math.c ****      * they are between -1456 and 1456 so the 16bit multiply does not overflow.
 326:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/lv_math.c ****      */
